    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_000&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こうして、
ふたりきりで会うのって
久しぶり、だね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's been some time since we've
been alone, hasn't it...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273684</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスと戦う前……
アーリィでお話して以来、
ですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We haven't talked like this since the
night before Dhaos's fight in Arlee... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えっと……そう、だっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh...It's been...that long?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれから……１年半も
経ったんですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>One year has passed since...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>１年半……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>One year...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……そうか。
もうそんなに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...That's right...regrettably...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕たち、本当に
これでいいのかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are we really okay being like this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さん……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...&lt;Cless&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦ってる時は
無我夢中だった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When we were fighting, I
got selfishly absorbed in...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>父さんたちの仇を取りたい、
使命を引き継ぎたいって
ずっと思ってた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>After father died, my mission
was all I could ever think of. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なのに、終わってみれば、
世界を救った英雄として、
まつりあげられて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And once everything was finally
over, the world branded me a 
hero" for some reason.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……&lt;Cless&gt;さんは、
英雄として、人々のために
がんばってます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...&lt;Cless&gt;, as a hero, you tried
your best for countless people. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私は……本当に
皆さんのご期待に
添えているのでしょうか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I...wonder...Am I honestly
helping people?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何言ってるんだ、&lt;Mint&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you saying, &lt;Mint&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君は十分にみんなの声を
聞いてるし、みんなに
喜ばれてるじゃないか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You listen to people's problems
and heal them. Aren't you
satisfied with that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275116</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……確かに法術師の力を
使えば、皆さんの体を
治すことはできます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I can certaintly heal people's
wounds, thanks to my use of 
the Divine Power.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275116</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、人の心までは
治せないんです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>However, people's hearts can't
simply be healed with spells.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mint&gt;……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mint&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんの
心ひとつだって……
私には治せない……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>To begin with, I can't even repair
the damage done to your heart...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな……僕は
君さえいれば……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's...not true! I'll always have you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Cless&gt;, that's...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……僕たちはどこへ
流されていくんだろう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I really wonder...where the world
will brush us away to... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どこへだって……
&lt;Cless&gt;さんと一緒なら
……私は平気ですよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It doesn't matter where we end up
or how bad it gets...As long as I'm
with you, I'll be all right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_060_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mint&gt;……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mint&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
